### USER NOTES ENDPOINTS ###

# GET all notes for current user
GET http://localhost:5000/notes

### Filter by status
GET http://localhost:5000/notes?status=pending

### GET specific note by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/notes/1

### POST send/upload an audio file
POST http://localhost:5000/notes/send
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="zamarzanie_wody.mp3"
Content-Type: audio/mpeg

< ../INPUT/audio_files/zamarzanie_wody.mp3
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--


### Process
POST http://localhost:5000/notes/process/1


### DELETE a note (user)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/notes/3

